        },
        {
            "id": 20,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   對，而且委託裡還提到，你確實已經擁有完整的寶藏資訊了？",
                "name": "格拉尼"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 21,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_003",
                "name2": "char_220_grani#3",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 22,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   打開寶藏必要的鑰匙和寶藏的位置，都是歷代村長口口相傳的秘密。",
                "name": "可蘿爾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 23,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   具體的我暫時還不能說......抱歉，我不是有意要向你隱瞞。",
                "name": "可蘿爾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 24,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_003",
                "name2": "char_220_grani#3",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 25,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   沒問題的，至少等到你完全相信我之後再說吧。",
                "name": "格拉尼"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 26,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_003",
                "name2": "char_220_grani#5",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 27,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   那些賞金獵人得知了這些情報，就一直在威脅著村民們。",
                "name": "可蘿爾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 28,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   他們破壞村子的田地，搶走越冬的儲糧，騷擾村民——如果那時我不站出來，村子就真的要完了。",
                "name": "可蘿爾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 29,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   只要讓他們知道寶藏的情報在我這裡，至少他們不再去傷害其他村民們了。",
                "name": "可蘿爾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 30,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_003",
                "name2": "char_220_grani#5",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 31,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   但就算你受了那樣的苦......",
                "name": "格拉尼"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 32,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_003",
                "name2": "char_220_grani#5",
                "focus": 1.0
